### Transaction Locking Module - HTTP Requests
### Port: 8089
### Transaction Locking Konuları (Optimistic, Pessimistic, Deadlock, Serialization Failure)

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8089
@contentType = application/json

### 38. Optimistic locking
### @Version alanı flush / commit sırasında kontrol edilir
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/locking/optimistic/1?newSalary=10000

###

### 39. Pessimistic locking
### PESSIMISTIC_WRITE lock transaction commit / rollback'te bırakılır
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/locking/pessimistic/1?newSalary=10000

###

### 40. Serialization failure
### SERIALIZABLE isolation'da DB conflict detection
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/locking/serialization/1?newSalary=10000

###

### 25. Deadlock testi
### Transaction isolation deadlock'a neden olabilir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/locking/deadlock-test?idA=1&idB=2

###

### 25. Deadlock çözümü - Consistent lock ordering
### Her zaman ID'ye göre sıralı kilitle
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/locking/deadlock-solution?id1=1&id2=2

